$ System.Security.Principal.IdentityReference

A `System.Security.Principal.IdentityReference` object represents an *identity*.

This class is the base class for
  • → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Security/Principal/NTAccount[`System.Security.Principal.NTAccount`]
  • → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Security/Principal/SecurityIdentifier[`System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier`]

{ Translate()

  The following → Windows/PowerShell scriptles try to demonstrate how an `NTAccount` can be translated (converted) to a `SecurityIdentifier` (→ Windows/security/SID), and vice versa.

